If there is a system problem to diagnose, where do you find system logs to download?
A. In the Events option of the System Console.
B. In the Problems option of the System Console.
C. In the Troubleshooting option of the System Console.
D. In the Infrastructure Map option of the System Console.

Which statement describes the correct procedure to grant user jane this access?
A. Grant jane the "Create new patterns" right under Workload Management.
B. Grant jane the "Manage all databases and client configurations (Full permission)" rights
under Workload Management.
C. Bring up the list of instances. Highlight the instance db2sdin9 and add user jane to the
